Well, since we are throwing silly ideas out....<P>Here is what I woudl like to see.<P>NOTE!: this is my personal opinion/ wish. it has never been posted elsewhere, nor might it ever be posted again.<P>Anyone who is doing our quests knows that we are fighting necromancy. as this story unfolds it turns out that many before us have fought the dark arts. more unsettling is the fact that many unmentionable ones have used the addage 'fight fire with fire'. So it is entirely plausible wihin the cantext of the game for us to develop necromantic abilities.<P>That being said.....<P>Let us charm what we can now, and add to that all undead. Our pet problems, dungeons included, are solved. this coudl even help some PvP spots, but not all. So what do we do?<P>I say when we encounter a dead PC, we have the option to raise them. NOW they are an NPC pet, and it forces their normal release. This woudl allow us to actually pull pets from the battlefields. <P>Imagine the decision one woudl have to make. Either wait and hold for a Rez, risking adding to the enemies forces, or release fast.<P>Sinister...<P>Dark....<P>Annoying to the enemy...<P><BR>BEAUTIFUL!<P>But again, that is just soemthing I woudl like to see. People already scream either<P>A) We are NOT EQ Necros...<P>B) We are NOT EQ Chanters...<P>or <P>C) we are TOO MUCH Like EQ necros or Chanters...<P>I say screw all that, this game needs real necromancers, and we shoudl be it. It is too happy, too clean. there is NO evil in this game, only percieved evil. Other than the foul humanoids, or the udnead, most of what we percieve to be enemy MOBs in our realm are actually friendly NPC types in the opposing realms. Druids and Filihds are not viewed nearly so poorly in Hibernia!<P>So let us be truly evil. <P>Only one Midgaard class comes close. The shadowblade worships Loki, the trickster. He was not technically evil, but far from good.<P>I can think on NOONE in Hibernia that fits the bill of evil.<P>Cabalists are FAR from evil. They follow the Khaballa (hence Cabalist, NOT from a Cabal) and create golems. they are jews, so quit hating on the rabbis of  Camelot you anti-semites!<P>Which leaves us.<P>We follow the ways of Merlin. Has Merlin ever been percieved as evil? Not by us for sure. We are more in line with the mind bending dark sorcerors of Arabian Nights (think Jafar). So yes, we are the closest to evil in he entire game, but following Merlin kinda makes this not be true. <P>So let us be evil then.<P>--------------------<P>i3ullseye<BR>"You're good, but me? I'm Magic!"<P>Rictus -Sorceror(DAOC)/Rictus(EQ)<BR>DAOC Sorceror team lead...<P>Please visit our <A HREF="http://www.yesterdayland.com/popopedia/shows/toys/ty1050.php" TARGET=_blank>Sponsors!</A>  <IMG SRC="biggrin.gif" border="0">
